%Hence, since $\psi_{1}[J]\in \Omega_{0}(K ( Z^{0}[J], <V(\frac{\delta}{\delta J_{x}})>_{x}))$ and
%$D$ is an endomorphism, it follows from (\ref{d.12}) that
